{"tid":972343,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"原來每日上兩個幾鐘連登","createTime":"2019-01-07T10:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T11:43:01.000Z","uid":41355,"like":9,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c5a52c48c0cb2c57eb478e09923849d187c9e705","tid":972343,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T10:20:25.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟 final year project 整左個 android app 出黎，可以 track 住每日用左啲咩app。<br />\n<br />\n整完梗係自己試下用啦，用左個幾禮拜，先至發現原來每日用成四個幾鐘電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又差唔多一半時間係上緊連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個 app 除左 daily 同 weekly report 之外仲有 reminder, white list 之類既功能<br />\n<br />\n新手寫野，一定有不足既地方，希望咁多位巴打屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B8ahTBc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB8ahTBc.png&h=92914c29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bxxW89w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbxxW89w.png&h=89874bca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VyCswnQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVyCswnQ.png&h=f30e2cfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1F2EG6A4tGtPUZoyIZiUwo0QUA8Fs8ciE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1F2EG6A4tGtPUZoyIZiUwo0QUA8Fs8ciE&d=6F2wiYdL7XsyXFQWHa%2BeTZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=f1459c25\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1F2EG6A4tGtPUZoyIZiUwo0QUA8Fs8ciE</a><br />\n<br />\n個 app 會收集番大家既使用數據黎做個 project part 2 既 analysis ，希望大家唔好裝完即 del 用耐啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c71b0c2def3d52f52c9b79655a98d6db5619beb","tid":972343,"uid":5793,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T10:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/12vNwvC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F12vNwvC.png&h=06a8b62d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nios用家表示一日用電話5個幾鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ffbe3db6968790230a5ba7984c9bd80be2529e","tid":972343,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T10:25:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j76AFpU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj76AFpU.png&h=9ed01e58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c61789154a7fc39580b54a3849a71e0353088ba","tid":972343,"uid":41355,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6c71b0c2def3d52f52c9b79655a98d6db5619beb","tid":972343,"uid":5793,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T10:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/12vNwvC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F12vNwvC.png&h=06a8b62d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nios用家表示一日用電話5個幾鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T11:35:42.000Z","msg":"連登已經碌到無野睇既地步<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c68e657abebf4eb0424bf0be7e3899a1b32a63a","tid":972343,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T12:16:26.000Z","msg":"成日以為樓主好大<br />\n原來而家先Final Year<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03707b0ec93970849afd7e4e01967cd3f586bc50","tid":972343,"uid":5793,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c61789154a7fc39580b54a3849a71e03530